### Global Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### 1. Test the Base Route (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Get All Jobs (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs/all
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. Apply for a Job WITHOUT a Token (Should Fail with 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs/apply/1
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 4. Apply for a Job WITH a Token (Example Format)
# Note: You will replace 'YOUR_MOCK_TOKEN' with an actual Firebase ID Token later.
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs/apply/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_MOCK_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json